---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy" description="How Selcurate uses cookies.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold font-heading text-foreground mb-6">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-foreground-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>

      <p>
        <strong>Essential:</strong> Cookie consent preference (remembers your choice).
        No opt-out available as this is required for the site to function.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Analytics (optional):</strong> Google Analytics 4 cookies (_ga, _ga_*)
        that help us understand site usage. These are only set AFTER you accept analytics
        cookies via the consent banner.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Affiliate tracking:</strong> When you click an affiliate link, the retailer
        (e.g., Amazon) sets their own cookies. These are governed by the retailer's cookie
        policy, not ours.
      </p>

      <h2>How Consent Works</h2>
      <p>
        When you first visit our site, you'll see a consent banner at the bottom of the page.
        You can choose to accept or reject analytics cookies. Your choice is stored in your
        browser's localStorage and remembered on future visits.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you reject analytics cookies, Google Analytics will not set any cookies or collect
        your IP address. The site functions normally either way.
      </p>

      <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        You can clear cookies in your browser settings at any time. To reset your consent
        preference, clear your browser's localStorage for selcurate.com. Rejecting analytics
        cookies does not affect your experience on this site.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We do not set third-party advertising cookies. Affiliate retailers may set their own
        cookies when you visit their sites through our links — these are subject to the
        retailer's own privacy and cookie policies.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
